short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Quickly Generate Skeleton UI to Boost Development Efficiency

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This browser extension is designed to help developers quickly generate skeleton UI templates with just a few clicks, saving time compared to manually designing interfaces. Whether you need to create a simple UI framework quickly or a flexible, this tool has you covered. The generated skeleton structures are lightweight and simple, perfect for web projects, helping you accelerate development and increase productivity.
